Hey there all, we have a great new offer for you guys.

SwiftVM is being run by two enthusiastic friends who have been working with systems, and worked for a few other hosts the last years. We have a high standard for our performance and therefor only use top grade SSD servers, or SSD cached servers, with speeds of over 1GB/s or 450MB/s for our cached nodes. We have been active since the beginning of '13, and gotten some great feedback from known members of the community.
